      <p>I love cooking with my kids! I mean not all the time because that&#8217;s insane, but I love that they&#8217;re getting a good base. I never want our kitchen to be seen as some intimidating place where you could ruin something. I have noticed that having 3 kids I need to make a special effort to include them one at a time and to respect their differing levels of confidence (they&#8217;re 1.5, 6, and 9).  </p>
