    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>My kids are 8 and 5 and they are in charge of dinner one night (we usually do every other week, definitely on a slow night). They love searching the Internet for recipes, crossing off their list at the market, and they think it&#8217;s hilarious to switch jobs with the adults (i.e.: mom and dad set the table and clear the dishes). It&#8217;s amazing to see them scurry around the kitchen and proudly present their &#8220;masterpiece.&#8221;  And I shouldn&#8217;t even use quotes because they truly are masterpieces!</p>
