    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>You are absolutely right about not to cook with children when you are in a hurry or when you dont want your kitchen to be dirty..haha! It will only make us nuts. My daughter is 3. From this reading i get the inspiration to involve her in some means of kitchen activities within a few months. Wish me good luck!</p>
    </div>

      </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-52713" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="http://theylivedontreacle.net" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Dormouse</a></cite></div>
